msgid ""
"Odoo can update the rates at regular intervals. To do so, change "
"the :guilabel:`Interval` from :guilabel:`Manually` "
"to :guilabel:`Daily`, :guilabel:`Weekly`, or :guilabel:`Monthly`. You can "
