#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:909
msgid "You can choose any Odoo journal to post the payslip entries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:910
msgid ""
"Configure the tax by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Taxes`. Create the necessary taxes for the Employment Hero payslip "
"entries. Fill in the tax code from **Employment Hero** in "
"the :guilabel:`Matching Employment Hero Tax` field."
msgstr ""
"Cấu hình thuế bằng cách vào :menuselection:`Kế toán --> Cấu hình --> Thuế`. "
"Tạo các loại thuế cần thiết cho các bút toán phiếu lương Employment Hero. "
"Điền mã thuế từ **Employment Hero** vào trường :guilabel:`Thuế Employment "
"Hero khớp`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:915
msgid "How does the API work?"
msgstr "API hoạt động như thế nào?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:917
msgid ""
"The API syncs the journal entries from Employment Hero to Odoo and leaves "
"them in draft mode. The reference includes the Employment Hero payslip entry "
"ID in brackets for the user to easily retrieve the same record in Employment "
"Hero and Odoo."
msgstr ""
"API đồng bộ hóa các bút toán từ Employment Hero sang Odoo và để chúng ở chế "
"độ nháp. Tham chiếu bao gồm ID bảng lương Employment Hero trong ngoặc vuông "
"để người dùng dễ dàng truy xuất cùng một bản ghi trong Employment Hero và "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:None
msgid ""
"Example of a Employment Hero Journal Entry in Odoo Accounting (Australia)"
msgstr "Ví dụ về záznam deníku Employment Hero v Odoo Accounting (Austrálie)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:924
msgid ""
"By default, the synchronisation happens once per week. You can fetch the "
"records manually by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings` and, in the :guilabel:`Enable Employment Hero Integration` "
"option, click on :guilabel:`Fetch Payruns Manually`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:928
msgid ""
"Employment Hero payslip entries also work based on double-entry bookkeeping."
msgstr ""
"Záznamy výplatních pásek Employment Hero také fungují na základě podvojného "
"účetnictví."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:930
msgid ""
"The accounts used by Employment Hero are defined in the "
"section :guilabel:`Payroll settings`."
msgstr ""
"Účty používané systémem Employment Hero jsou definovány v sekci "
":guilabel:`Nastavení mezd`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:None
msgid "Chart of Accounts menu in Employment Hero"
msgstr "Nabídka účtové osnovy v Employment Hero"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:935
msgid ""
"For the API to work, you need to create the same accounts as the default "
"accounts of your Employment Hero business (**same name and same code**) in "
"Odoo. You also need to choose the correct account types in Odoo to generate "
"accurate financial reports."
